sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant App as App.tsx
    participant API as api.ts
    participant Ctrl as Controller
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as SQLite
    
    Browser->>App: 1. User navigates to home page
    App->>API: 2. useEffect calls api.getAll()
    API->>Ctrl: 3. GET /api/touristpoints?page=1&pageSize=10&search=...
    Ctrl->>Repo: 4. GetAll(page, pageSize, search)
    Repo->>DB: 5. SQL Query (EF Core)
    DB-->>Repo: 6. Returns IEnumerable<TouristPoint>
    Repo-->>Ctrl: 7. Build response with pagination metadata
    Ctrl-->>API: 8. HTTP 200 OK
    API-->>App: 9. Returns PaginatedResponse
    App-->>Browser: 10. Update state & render list
